// only for setup, set to 1==1 to run
if ( 1==1 ) {
clear all

// cd C:
cd /Users/mas/Dropbox/OET
use "oetaug2010_pitstoplevel_v8.dta", clear

sort subjectid pitstopid


gen pse = psexpectation / 1000
gen female = 0
replace female = 1 if gender == 1

gen age2 = age*age

replace winpc = 2^-100 if winpc == 0
sum winpc
}


#delimit ;

tw  (lpolyci pse winpc , 
        kernel(gaussian) bwidth(0.015) degree(1) 
	    msymbol(none)
  	    lcolor(gs10)
  	    alwidth(0.0001)
  	    )
    (scatter pse winpc , msize(1) mlwidth(0.1) jitter(3) msymbol(+) mcolor(gs11) mfcolor(gs11) )
    (lpoly pse winpc, 
        kernel(gaussian) bwidth(0.015) degree(1) 
  	    msymbol(none)
  	    lcolor(black)
  	    lwidth(0.6)
  	    )
  	(function y=x, lpattern(shortdash) lcolor(black) lwidth(0.3) )
  	, 
  	note("")
  	legend(off) 
    xtitle("obj. prob.") 
    ytitle("subj. prob.")
  	aspect(1) 
  	scheme(s1mono)
  	xla(0(0.1)1, grid) yla(0(0.1)1, angle(horizontal) grid) plotregion(margin(none));

#delimit cr


gr export oet_first_paper/figures/kernel.eps, replace
gr export oet_first_paper/figures/kernel.png, replace


forvalues r = 1/6 {

#delimit ;

tw  (lpolyci pse winpc if racenum == `r', 
        kernel(gaussian) bwidth(0.02) degree(1) 
	    msymbol(none)
  	    lcolor(gs10)
  	    alwidth(0.0001)
  	    )
    (scatter pse winpc if racenum == `r', msize(1) mlwidth(0.1) jitter(1) msymbol(+) mcolor(gs6) mfcolor(black) )
    (lpoly pse winpc if racenum == `r', 
        kernel(gaussian) bwidth(0.02) degree(1) 
  	    msymbol(none)
  	    lcolor(black)
  	    lwidth(0.6)
  	    )
  	(function y=x, lpattern(shortdash) lcolor(black) lwidth(0.3) )
  	, 
  	title("Race `r'")
  	note("")
  	legend(off) 
    xtitle("obj. prob.") 
    ytitle("subj. prob.")
  	name( race`r') 
  	aspect(1) 
  	scheme(s1mono)
  	xla(0(0.1)1, grid) yla(0(0.1)1, angle(horizontal) grid) plotregion(margin(none));

#delimit cr

}

#delimit ;
gr combine race1 race2 race3 race4 race5 race6, 
   xcommon ycommon altshrink
       
;

gr export oet_first_paper/figures/kernelallraces.eps, replace;
gr export oet_first_paper/figures/kernelallraces.png, replace;
